graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Dashboard Component"
        Frontend[Frontend - React 18 SPA<br/>PatternFly 6 UI<br/>Redux State Management]
        Backend[Backend - Fastify<br/>Node.js 20<br/>REST API Server]
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>Sidecar Container<br/>TLS Termination]
        ModuleFed[Module Federation<br/>Webpack 5<br/>Dynamic Plugin System]
        K8sClient[Kubernetes Client<br/>@kubernetes/client-node<br/>API Integration]
        WebSocket[WebSocket Server<br/>Real-time Updates]

        Frontend -->|API calls| Backend
        OAuthProxy -->|proxy| Backend
        Backend -->|uses| K8sClient
        Backend -->|manages| WebSocket
        Frontend -->|loads| ModuleFed
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources Managed"
        OdhApp[OdhApplication CR<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        DashConfig[OdhDashboardConfig CR<br/>opendatahub.io/v1alpha]
        OdhDoc[OdhDocument CR<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        QuickStart[OdhQuickStart CR<br/>console.openshift.io/v1]
        HwProfile[HardwareProfile CR<br/>infrastructure.opendatahub.io/v1]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>Authentication]
        Prometheus[Prometheus/Thanos<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH Integrations"
        ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator<br/>DataScienceCluster]
        Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks<br/>Notebook CRs]
        KServe[KServe<br/>InferenceService]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>ModelRegistry CRs]
        Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Pipeline Runs]
        Workbenches[Workbenches<br/>Notebook Instances]
    end

    subgraph "Dynamic Plugins"
        GenAI[Gen AI Plugin<br/>LLM Management]
        ModelReg[Model Registry Plugin<br/>Versioning]
        FeatureStore[Feature Store Plugin<br/>Engineering]
        LMEval[LM Eval Plugin<br/>Benchmarking]
    end

    User[User Browser] -->|HTTPS 443<br/>TLS 1.2+| OAuthProxy
    Backend -->|ServiceAccount Token| K8sAPI
    OAuthProxy -->|OAuth Flow| OAuthServer
    Backend -->|Query metrics| Prometheus

    K8sClient -->|Create/Read| OdhApp
    K8sClient -->|Manage| DashConfig
    K8sClient -->|Read| OdhDoc
    K8sClient -->|Read| QuickStart
    K8sClient -->|Read| HwProfile

    Backend -->|Read| ODHOperator
    Backend -->|Create/Manage| Notebooks
    Backend -->|Read status| KServe
    Backend -->|Manage| ModelRegistry
    Backend -->|Integrate| Pipelines
    Backend -->|Manage| Workbenches

    ModuleFed -.->|dynamic load| GenAI
    ModuleFed -.->|dynamic load| ModelReg
    ModuleFed -.->|dynamic load| FeatureStore
    ModuleFed -.->|dynamic load| LMEval

